-- Power Shortage at Gatwick Airport Disrupts Baggage System
-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 2012-03-10T13:28:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-10/power-shortage-at-gatwick-airport-disrupts-baggage-system.html
A power shortage at Gatwick
Airport’s North Terminal disrupted the baggage-handling system
this morning, according to the airport’s Twitter account.  Extra staff were brought in to manually move the bags and
engineers have since restored power, the airport said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sarah Jones in London at 
